ns%20rely%20on%20the%20execution%20of%20employees%20changing%20their%20processes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Wall%20Street's%20top%20bosses%20just%20gave%20a%20revealing%20look%20into%20how%20AI%20is%20changing%20the%20lives%20of%20bankers%20and%20analysts%20in%20its%20investment%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETen%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20Goldman%20wanted%20to%20win%20the%20business%20of%20a%20company%20going%20public%2C%20it%20would%20appoint%20a%20team%20of%20about%20half%20a%20dozen%20people%20who%20over%20two%20weeks%20would%20draft%20a%20prospectus%20known%20as%20an%20S-1%2C%20a%20significant%20regulatory%20document%20that%20details%20the%20business%2C%20financials%2C%20and%20risk%20factors%2C%20among%20other%20things.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20show%20would-be%20clients%20all%20the%20thought%20and%20legwork%20Goldman%20bankers%20had%20already%20put%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20you%20can%20basically%20have%20something%20that's%2095%25%20of%20the%20way%20there%20in%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20David%20Solomon%20said%20at%20Cisco's%20AI%20Summit%20on%20Wednesday.%20If%20the%2095%25%20is%20%26quot%3Bnow%20a%20commodity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20the%20remaining%205%25%20matters%20a%20lot%20because%20it's%20the%20margin%20where%20Goldman%20can%20get%20an%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20big%20deal%2C%20as%20Goldman%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20banks%20that%20take%20companies%20public%2C%20along%20with%20Morgan%20Stanley%20and%20JPMorgan.%20It's%20also%20just%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20Goldman%20is%20using%20AI%20to%20reduce%20grunt%20work%20and%20move%20more%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolomon%20described%20a%20road%20map%20for%20how%20Goldman%20Sachs%20was%20strategizing%20around%20AI.%20He%20said%20that%20getting%20engineers%20to%20free%20up%20capacity%20by%20being%2030%25%20more%20productive%20with%20coding%20tasks%20was%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20and%20most%20obvious%2C%26quot%3B%20given%20that%20Goldman%20has%2011%2C000%20engineers.%20Another%20priority%20is%20making%20better%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-data-neema-raphael-strategy-ai-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoldman's%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20includes%20tracking%20the%20firm's%20trades%20over%20the%20past%2040%20years%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-goldman-sachs-nasdaq-public-cloud-partnerships-deal-tech-strategy-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20it%20available%20to%20clients%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%2C%20and%20perhaps%20most%20visible%20and%20directly%20client-facing%2C%20is%20deploying%20AI%20in%20the%20investment-banking%20business.%20Enabling%20the%20bank%20to%20do%20more%20work%20by%20giving%20workers%20a%20kind%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-finance-giants-goldman-sachs-blackstone-perfect-search-generative-ai-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einformation%20superintelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20boost%20the%20already%20booming%20firm%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-compensation-pay-ceo-david-solomon-john-waldron-retention-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrought%20in%20more%20than%20%2453%20billion%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20using%20AI%20to%20draft%20IPO%20prospectuses%20to%20court%20potential%20clients%2C%20Solomon%20said%20Goldman%20was%20%26quot%3Bfocused%20on%20how%20we%20can%20completely%20change%20kind%20of%20what%20you'd%20call%20the%20material%20preparation%26quot%3B%20involved%20in%20investment%20banking.%20That%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldmans-sachs-george-lee-ai-tools-for-workforce-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincludes%20preparing%20bankers%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20client%20meetings%20and%20getting%20information%20to%20clients%20to%20better%20make%20investment%20decisions.%20He%20said%20Goldman%20was%20also%20building%20an%20%26quot%3Binvestment-banking%20copilot%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20bank's%20own%20data.%20Copilots%20typically%20describe%20AI%20tools%20that%20help%20workers%20be%20more%20productive%20by%20drafting%20text%2C%20analyzing%20information%2C%20and%20suggesting%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20bankers%20who%20can%20anticipate%20changes%20to%20their%20daily%20processes.%20The%20Goldman%20CEO%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20AI%20to%20shake%20up%20analyst%20workflows%20in%20equity%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20things%20analysts%20and%20their%20dedicated%20teams%20do%20is%20report%20on%20companies%20and%20feed%20that%20information%20into%20models%2C%20often%20to%20gauge%20a%20company's%20trajectory%2C%20growth%2C%20and%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%20that%20can%20all%20be%20automated%20now%20with%20this%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Solomon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20those%20jobs%20will%20be%20replaced%20with%20technology.%20%26quot%3BYou%20really%20need%20the%20analysts%2C%20and%20you%20need%20smaller%20teams%2C%20and%20you%20need%20a%20horizontal%20engine%20that%20basically%20does%20all%20that%20work%20for%20everyone%20as%20opposed%20to%20individual%20pods%20for%20every%20single%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Solomon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20these%20AI%20deployments%20will%20rely%20in%20part%20on%20the%20execution%20of%20change%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolomon%20said%20that%20generating%20efficiencies%20and%20cutting%20down%20on%20redundancies%20in%20the%20equity-research%20example%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20massive%20process%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%2C%20because%20people%20don't%20want%20to%20change%20their%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Solomon%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20like%20their%20team.%20They%20like%20the%20fact%20they%20have%20complete%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E