%20being%20handed%20fines%20or%20prosecuted%20for%20their%20actions%2C%20train%20companies%20in%20Britain%20have%20been%20urged%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn018nrdyx7o%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereport.%20Rail%20watchdog%20Transport%20Focus%20suggested%20that%20the%20train%20companies%20introduce%20a%20novel%20system%20that%20%26quot%3Bmakes%20things%20fairer%20for%20everyone%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suggestion%20comes%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20multiple%20cases%20where%20passengers%20were%20forced%20into%20lengthy%20legal%20proceedings%20over%20small%20amounts%20of%20money.%20Last%20year%2C%2022-year-old%20Sam%20Williamson%20was%20threatened%20with%20prosecution%20by%20train%20operator%2C%20Northern%20Rail%2C%20after%20he%20mistakenly%20bought%20an%20invalid%20%C2%A33.65%20(Rs%20385.22)%20ticket%20using%20his%2016-25%20railcard.%20The%20full%20price%20of%20the%20ticket%20was%20%C2%A35.50%20(Rs%20580.46)%20-%20%C2%A31.85%20(rs%20195.25)%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Williamson's%20case%20prompted%20widespread%20criticism%20of%20Northern%20Rail%20which%20was%20forced%20to%20withdraw%20all%20live%20prosecutions%20against%20the%20passenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTransport%20Focus%20has%20long%20been%20concerned%20about%20the%20complexity%20of%20rail%20fares%20and%20ticketing%2C%20particularly%20for%20passengers%20who%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20buy%20the%20right%20ticket%20for%20their%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.transportfocus.org.uk%2Fnews%2Frevenue-protection-priorities-to-improve-passenger-experience%2F%5C%22%3Eread%20%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20statement%20by%20Natasha%20Grice%2C%20director%20for%20rail%20at%20Transport%20Focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20and%20support%20the%20principle%20that%20all%20users%20of%20rail%20should%20be%20paying%20for%20their%20ticket%2C%20but%20we%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20passengers%20who%20make%20an%20innocent%20mistake%20aren't%20punished%20unfairly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fancient-pagan-temple-linked-to-jesus-ancestors-found-under-jerusalem-7497671%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Ancient%20Pagan%20Temple%20Linked%20To%20Jesus'%20Ancestors%20Found%20Under%20Jerusalem%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EReview%20underway%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20for%20Transport%20(DfT)%20has%20already%20ordered%20the%20Office%20of%20Rail%20and%20Road%20to%20carry%20out%20an%20independent%20review%20of%20rail%20fare%20prosecutions%20and%20enforcement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20ordered%20a%20review%20of%20revenue%20protection%20practices%20which%20will%20look%20at%20what%20changes%20can%20be%20made%2C%20and%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20have%20been%20clear%20with%20train%20operators%20that%20their%20policies%20on%20ticketing%20must%20be%20fair%20and%20easy%20to%20understand%20at%20all%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20DfT%20spokesman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%20watchdog's%20suggestion%20for%20a%20nationwide%20implementation%2C%20rail%20companies%20such%20as%20Cross%20Country%20and%20Southeastern%20have%20already%20introduced%20yellow%20card%20systems.%20The%20Merseyside%20Rail%20is%20also%20looking%20to%20introduce%20the%20move%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737129960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fu0ejbfn_uk_625x300_17_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcaught-ticketless-rail-fines-could-turn-into-yellow-cards-in-uk-7498070%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20suggestion%20comes%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20multiple%20cases%20where%20passengers%20were%20forced%20into%20lengthy%20legal%20pro