20attack%20by%20an%20intruder%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20on%20Thursday.%20He%20suffered%20multiple%20wounds.%20The%20Mumbai%20Police%20has%20recorded%20the%20statement%20of%20his%20wife%20and%20actor%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20observing%20his%20progress%20and%20he%20is%20doing%20excellently%20well%20according%20to%20our%20expectations.%20As%20per%20his%20progress%2C%20we%20have%20advised%20him%20bed%20rest%20and%20if%20he%20is%20comfortable%2C%20then%20in%20two%20to%20three%20days%20we%20will%20discharge%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Nitin%20Dange%2C%20neurosurgeon%20at%20Lilavati%20Hospital%2C%20adding%20a%20team%20of%20doctors%20checked%20on%20him%20and%20made%20him%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20is%20fit%20to%20be%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20intensive%20care%20unit%20(ICU)%20and%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20shifting%20him%20to%20a%20special%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20neurosurgeon%2C%20who%20led%20the%20team%20of%20doctors%20who%20operated%20on%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKhan%20had%20three%20injuries%2C%20two%20on%20the%20hand%20and%20one%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20neck.%20And%20the%20major%20part%20was%20at%20the%20back%2C%20which%20was%20in%20the%20spine%2C%20thoracic%20spine%20we%20call.%20A%20sharp%20object%20was%20lodged%20inside%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20very%20deep%2C%20touching%20the%20dura%20and%20the%20spinal%20cord%2C%20but%20it%20has%20not%20damaged%20the%20spinal%20cord%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Dange%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20have%20removed%20the%20sharp%20object%2C%20the%20doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20stairs%20at%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20home%20clearly%20showed%20the%20suspect%20wearing%20a%20red%20scarf%20and%20carrying%20a%20backpack.%20The%20suspect%20scurried%20down%20the%20stairs%20from%20the%20sixth%20floor%20of%20'Satguru%20Sharan'%20building%2C%20where%20the%20Khans%20live%2C%20at%202.30%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20has%20been%20arrested%20yet.%20Over%2030%20teams%20have%20been%20formed%20to%20track%20and%20arrest%20the%20suspect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20(Urban)%20Yogesh%20Kadam%20said%20robbery%20was%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20attack%2C%20adding%20no%20underworld%20gang%20was%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737129300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F1du3svcg_saif-attacker_625x300_17_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-photo-of-saif-case-suspect-surfaces-had-changed-clothes-after-attack-7497445%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20CCTV%20grab%20of%20the%20suspect%20who%20attacked%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20at%20the%20actor's%20Mumbai%20home%20has%20surfaced%2C%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-photo-of-saif-case-suspect-surfaces-had-changed-clothes-after-attack-7497445%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fadnavis%20assures%20culprit%20in%20Saif%20attack%20will%20be%20caught%20soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737129163000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117338241%2Cimgsize-50298.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmaharashtra-cm-devendra-fadnavis-assures-culprit-in-saif-ali-khan-attack-will-be-caught-soon-police-have-got-many-clues%2Farticleshow%2F117338210.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117338210.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20assured%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20police%20have%20gathered%20significant%20clues%20in%20the%20stabbing%20case%20of