20last%20year%20after%20a%20life-threatening%20road%20accident%20at%202022-end%2C%20Pant%20made%20a%20fabulous%20comeback%20to%20Test%20cricket%20after%20securing%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title%20in%20Barbados.%20Scoring%20a%20century%20in%20his%20comeback%20Test%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20Chennai%20in%20September%2C%20Pant%20made%20677%20runs%20in%2010%20matches%20and%2019%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2037.61%20during%20the%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%20cycle%20of%202023-25.%20This%20also%20includes%20a%20century%20and%20four%20fifties%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20109.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20last%20participated%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20back%20in%20the%202017%2F18%20edition%2C%20playing%20his%20last%20match%20against%20Vidarbha%20in%20the%20final%20at%20Indore.%20He%20had%20led%20Delhi%20to%20the%20finals%20as%20captain%20but%20could%20not%20win%20them%20the%20title.%20He%20scored%2021%20and%2032%20runs%20in%20the%20title%20clash%20as%20Vidarbha%20won%20by%20nine%20wickets%20in%20a%20one-sided%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20seven%20matches%20in%20the%20tournament%20back%20then%2C%20Pant%20scored%20315%20runs%20in%20nine%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2035.00%2C%20with%20a%20solitary%20half-century%20and%20best%20score%20of%2099.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20return%20will%20boost%20Delhi's%20form%2C%20currently%20sitting%20at%20fourth%20spot%20in%20their%20group%20with%20a%20win%2C%20loss%20and%20three%20draws%2C%20giving%20them%2014%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Star%20India%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20added%20to%20the%20Delhi%20squad%20for%20their%20upcoming%20Ranji%20Trophy%20clashes%2C%20but%20his%20playing%20is%20dependent%20on%20his%20availability%2C%20said%20the%20sources%20in%20the%20Delhi%20and%20District%20Cricket%20Association%20(DDCA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20said%20that%20while%20Virat%20is%20not%20likely%20to%20play%20the%20first%20match%20against%20Saurashtra%20in%20Group%20D%2C%20starting%20from%20January%2023%20in%20Rajkot%2C%20he%20could%20join%20the%20team%20for%20the%20second%20match%20against%20Railways%20starting%20from%20January%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20on%20Virat's%20availability%20comes%20when%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20has%20taken%20a%20much%20harder%20stance%20regarding%20the%20participation%20of%20Indian%20international%20stars%20in%20domestic%20cricket.%20In%20a%20new%20policy%20released%20on%20Thursday%2C%20it%20made%20it%20%26quot%3Bmandatory%26quot%3B%20to%20participate%20in%20domestic%20matches%20to%20remain%20%26quot%3Beligible%26quot%3B%20for%20selection%20in%20the%20national%20team%20and%20for%20the%20central%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20policy%2C%20BCCI%20stated%20that%20taking%20part%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20will%20remain%20connected%20to%20the%20cricket%20ecosystem.%20The%20statement%20added%20that%20any%20exceptions%20to%20taking%20part%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20will%20be%20considered%20only%20under%20extraordinary%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParticipation%20in%20Domestic%20Matches%20is%20mandatory%20for%20players%20to%20remain%20eligible%20for%20selection%20in%20the%20national%20team%20and%20for%20central%20contracts%2C%20as%20per%20BCCI%20guidelines.%20This%20policy%20ensures%20that%20players%20remain%20connected%20to%20the%20domestic%20cricket%20ecosystem%2C%20fostering%20talent%20development%2C%20maintaining%20match%20fitness%2C%20and%20strengthening%20the%20overall%20domestic%20structure.%20It%20also%20inspires%20emerging%20players%20by%20providing%20them%20opportunities%20to%20compete%20alongside%20top%20cricketers%2C%20ensuring%20continuity%20in%20talent%20progression.%20Any%20exceptions%20to%20this%20mandate%20will%20be%20considered%20only%20under%20extraordinary%20circumstances%20and%20will%20require%20formal%20notification%20and%20approval%20from%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Selection%20Committee%2C%20ensuring%20fairness%20and%20transparency%20in%20the%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20BCCI%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Team%20India%20conceded%20a%20disappointing%203-1%20defeat%20to%20Australia%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%202024-25%20and%20lost%20the%20opportunity%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20Final%20at%20Lord's.%20Also%2C%20before%20this%2C%20their%200-3%20whitewash%20to%20New%20Zealand%20at%20home%20before%20the%20Australia%20tour%20led%20to%20debates%20if%20international%20stars%20should%20play%20domestic%20cricket%20regularly%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20reunited%20with%20Mumbai's%20squad%20for%20their%20training%20sessions%20ahead%20of%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%202024-25%20Ranji%20Trophy%2C%20according%20to%20ESPNcricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20confirmed%20his%20availability%20for%20Punjab's%20upcoming%20Ranji%20Trophy%20sixth-round%20fixture%20against%20Karnataka%2C%20set%20to%20begin%20on%20January%2023%20at%20the%20M%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737127980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fhf80aajo_virat-kohli-rishabh-pant-afp_625x300_16_January