n%20recent%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20some%20of%20those%20recent%20polls%20-%20Maharashtra%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20particular%2C%20in%20each%20of%20which%20the%20BJP%20scored%20dominant%20wins%20on%20the%20back%20of%20women-centric%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20financial%20freebies%20-%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20women%20voters%20to%20winning%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20over%2046%20per%20cent%20-%20around%2071%20lakh%20-%20of%20Delhi's%20registered%20voters%20are%20women%2C%20with%20more%20signing%20up%20daily%2C%20according%20to%20the%20national%20capital's%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer.%20Last%20week%20the%20city's%20top%20poll%20official%20also%20said%20more%20women%20were%20registering%20to%20vote%2C%20ahead%20of%20this%20election%2C%20than%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20main%20parties%20in%20the%202025%20race%20in%20Delhi%20seem%20to%20have%20recognised%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20has%20announced%20women-specific%20schemes%20and%20sops%3B%20the%20AAP%20said%20it%20would%20give%20women%20Rs%202%2C100%20every%20month%2C%20after%20which%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20upped%20it%20to%20Rs%202%2C500.%20All%20three%20have%20also%20made%20other%20promises%2C%20from%20cash%20assistance%20to%20pregnant%20women%20and%20free%20travel%20for%20women%20in%20state-run%20buses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAP's%20Poll%20Special%20For%20Women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%20kicked%20things%20off%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20boss%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20forced%20to%20quit%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20while%20he%20battles%20corruption%20charges%2C%20said%20his%20party%20would%20give%20Rs%202%2C100%20to%20Delhi%20women%20as%20direct%20cash%20transfers%20every%20month%2C%20if%20they%20voted%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20to%20make%20two%20big%20announcements...%20both%20are%20for%20women.%20I%20had%20earlier%20promised%20to%20give%20Rs%201%2C