een%20credited%20with%20a%20key%20role%20in%20helping%20it%20win%20that%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Pregnant%20Women%20Outreach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20hoping%20that%20attention%20to%20pregnant%20women%20will%20pay%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20boss%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20announcing%20the%20manifesto%20on%20Friday%2C%20promised%20pregnant%20women%20a%20one-time%20payment%20of%20Rs%2021%2C000%20in%20addition%20Rs%205%2C000%20for%20the%20first%20child%20and%20Rs%206%2C000%20for%20the%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-21-000-for-pregnant-women-rs-500-subsidy-on-lpg-cylinders-in-bjps-manifesto-for-delhi-polls-7494867%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20BJP's%20Delhi%20Manifesto%2C%20Rs%2021%2C000%20Aid%20For%20Pregnant%20Women%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20announced%20a%20scheme%20that%20will%20pay%20women%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'In%20First%20Cabinet%20Meeting'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20these%20promises%20will%20be%20implemented%2C%20each%20party%20has%20vowed%2C%20in%20the%20very%20first%20cabinet%20meeting%20after%20the%20new%20government%20is%20formed.%20And%20these%20promises%2C%20election%20analysts%20have%20told%20NDTV%2C%20could%20be%20one%20very%20real%20reason%20behind%20women%20rushing%20to%20register%20to%20vote%20next%20month.%20And%20where%20those%20votes%20will%20land%20could%2C%20in%20a%20very%20real%20sense%2C%20decide%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%202025%20Delhi%20Assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reception%20to%20these%20overtures%20has%20been%20mixed%2C%20with%20most%20welcoming%20the%20initiatives%20(regardless%20of%20the%20party%20making%20the%20assurance)%20and%20some%20questioning%20the%20sustainability%20and%20long-term%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20have%20pointed%20out%20that